<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/193290-what-is-the-significance-of-the-buddha">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[What is the significance of the Buddha laughing in the attic? Why was it left there? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_193290'><a id="like_count_community_question_193290" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/193290?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F10464963-the-buddha-in-the-attic">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/193290-what-is-the-significance-of-the-buddha">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/193290-what-is-the-significance-of-the-buddha">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
